{{!--
    Shared panel-header title — the icon + label span that every panel wrapper
    (panel.hbs / collapsible-panel.hbs / vital-panel-shell.hbs) renders identically.
    Extracting it here means the canonical gold-gothic title styling and the
    per-system icon-accent variant chain live in exactly ONE place, so the three
    wrappers can never drift apart again (#291).

    The wrappers still own their own header BAR (background, padding, toggle
    affordance, count badge placement, status badges) because those genuinely
    differ by interaction model — this partial owns only the title span itself.

    Hash arguments:
        label             — header title text (required).
        icon              — Font Awesome class (e.g. "fa-shield-alt"). Optional; omitted
                            icons leave the title text flush.
        iconAccent        — optional CSS color string applied inline to the icon, used
                            by collapsible panels that pass a per-panel accent colour.
        titleClass        — optional extra utility classes appended to the title span
                            (e.g. "tw-tracking-[0.02em] tw-min-w-0").
        labelAction       — optional data-action name. When present the label text is
                            wrapped in a button that fires the named action on click.
                            The button stops click propagation so the parent header's
                            data-toggle is NOT triggered alongside the action (#35).
        labelActionTitle  — optional tooltip for the label-action button (localised
                            string passed from the caller).
--}}
<span class="wh40k-panel-title tw-flex-1 tw-flex tw-items-center tw-gap-2 tw-font-display tw-text-[1.1rem] tw-font-semibold tw-text-[color:var(--wh40k-gold)] tw-whitespace-nowrap tw-overflow-hidden tw-text-ellipsis{{#if titleClass}} {{titleClass}}{{/if}}">
    {{#if icon}}<i class="fas {{icon}} tw-text-[color:var(--panel-accent,var(--wh40k-accent-gold))] bc:tw-text-crimson-light dh1:tw-text-gold-raw-l5 dh2:tw-text-gold-raw dw:tw-text-accent-combat ow:tw-text-brass-l20 rt:tw-text-gold im:tw-text-failure tw-flex-shrink-0"{{#if iconAccent}} style="color: {{iconAccent}};"{{/if}}></i> {{/if}}{{#if labelAction}}<button type="button" class="tw-bg-transparent tw-border-0 tw-p-0 tw-[font:inherit] tw-text-inherit tw-cursor-pointer hover:tw-opacity-80" data-action="{{labelAction}}"{{#if labelActionTitle}} title="{{labelActionTitle}}"{{/if}} onclick="event.stopPropagation()">{{label}}</button>{{else}}{{label}}{{/if}}
</span>
